I use the command below

  1. bazel clean
  2. bazel build -c opt --config=x86 //tensorflow/examples/android:tensorflow_demo
  3. sudo find / ./ -name libtensorflow_demo.so

the search result is below, where I didn't notice the "x86" version is generated ?!
